National Oil of Kenya Appoints Athmani as Chief Executive

-- B y   E r i c   O m b o k
-- 
2011-04-05T13:00:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-05/national-oil-of-kenya-appoints-athmani-as-chief-executive-1-.html
National Oil Corp. of Kenya , a
state-owned company that coordinates oil exploration in the East
African nation and supplies 30 percent of its crude, confirmed
Sumayya Hassan Athmani as its chief executive officer.  Athmani was appointed acting managing director of the
company in September 2010, it said in an e-mailed statement
today from Nairobi, the capital. Athmani joined the corporation
in 2004 as a company secretary and legal manager before rising
to the position of deputy managing director in 2007.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eric Ombok in Nairobi at 
 eombok@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  